\n<About The Forest Of Carnal Hell>Rui must advance through the
otherworldly realm known as "Roots," fending off
the demons she has encountered in the past, and
clear the game by defeating the boss.

\n<About The Forest Of Carnal Hell>Even if Rui is defeated, she will
ultimately be sent back to Tuberose.

\n<System>It will be difficult to clear it in one go.
Collect status-boosting items along the way and
strengthen Rui.
\n<System>Would you like to see the explanation again?
